  09 Jun 2015; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Updating remote-id in metadata.xml

  30 Jul 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  dfu-programmer-0.5.4-r1.ebuild, dfu-programmer-0.6.1.ebuild,
  dfu-programmer-0.6.2.ebuild:
  Use shorter get_udevdir() instead of the longer deprecated udev_get_udevdir()
  version.

*dfu-programmer-0.6.2 (27 Nov 2013)

  27 Nov 2013; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> +dfu-programmer-0.6.2.ebuild:
  Version bump, as requested by Wolfram Schlich in bug #492598.

*dfu-programmer-0.6.1 (08 May 2013)

  08 May 2013; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> +dfu-programmer-0.6.1.ebuild:
  Version bump #468746 by Priit Laes.

  11 Dec 2012; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  dfu-programmer-0.5.4-r1.ebuild:
  Use virtual/udev instead of sys-fs/udev. Use udev.eclass to determine correct
  rules.d path.

*dfu-programmer-0.5.4-r1 (15 Nov 2012)

  15 Nov 2012; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> -dfu-programmer-0.5.4.ebuild,
  +dfu-programmer-0.5.4-r1.ebuild:
  Incorporate review comments by Mike "vapier" Frysinger on #gentoo-dev. libusb
  should be slotted, emake install call was equivalent to default and udev
  rules are the exception to the never hardcode /lib rule.

